value.0: Long ago, mind flayers conquered and captured a clan of dwarves known as the Duergar from the dwarven kingdom of Shanatar.  After decades of torture and enslavement (including experimentation) in the hands of the illithids, the gray dwarves (or duergar) gained their freedom from their masters after an uprising.  However, they emerged as a bitter, twisted race, though they retained many of the augmented powers they gained through the tests.
